               WHEN COND-XIAA0019-OK
      *             차주번호
                    MOVE  XIAA0019-O-CUNIQNO
                      TO  WK-BRWR-NO
      *             차주고객명
                    MOVE  XIAA0019-O-CUSTNM1
                      TO  WK-BRWR-CUSTNM
               WHEN OTHER
                    DISPLAY 'S3500 IAA0019 CALL ERROR  = '
                             WK-H-O-BRWR-CUST-IDNFR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3500-IAA0019-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.

      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
      *@   모기업법인고객정보 조회
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3510-IAA0019-SELECT-RTN.

            INITIALIZE       XIAA0019-CA

      *    고객식별자 조회
      *    영역구분'B':은행, 'C':CARD
           MOVE  'B'
             TO  XIAA0019-I-SCOP-DSTIC
      *    모기업법인고객식별자
           MOVE  WK-H-O-MAMA-C-CUST-IDNFR
             TO  XIAA0019-I-CUST-IDNFR

      *@1  고객정보번호를　조회한다
           #DYCALL  IAA0019
                    YCCOMMON-CA
                    XIAA0019-CA

      *@1  호출결과 확인
           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN COND-XIAA0019-OK
      *             모기업법인번호
                    MOVE  XIAA0019-O-CUNIQNO
                      TO  WK-MAMA-BRWR-NO
      *             모기업고객명
                    MOVE  XIAA0019-O-CUSTNM1
                      TO  WK-MAMA-CRCS-NAME
               WHEN OTHER
                    DISPLAY 'S3510 IAA0019 CALL ERROR  = '
                             WK-H-O-MAMA-C-CUST-IDNFR
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3510-IAA0019-SELECT-EXT.
           EXIT.
