           MOVE WK-MAMA-BRWR-NO             TO OT-MAMA-BRWR-NO

      *   모기업고객식별자
           MOVE WK-H-O-MAMA-C-CUST-IDNFR    TO OT-MAMA-C-CUST-IDNFR

