      *@   CURSOR CLOSE
      *-----------------------------------------------------------------
       S3800-KJL0042-CLOSE-RTN.

           EXEC SQL
              CLOSE  THKJL0042_CUR
           END-EXEC

           EVALUATE  SQLCODE
               WHEN  CO-OK
                     CONTINUE
               WHEN  OTHER
                     MOVE 'KJL0042'    TO  XZUGEROR-I-TBL-ID
                     MOVE 'CLOSE'      TO  XZUGEROR-I-FUNC-CD
                     MOVE  SQLCODE     TO  XZUGEROR-I-SQL-CD
                     MOVE 'CURSOR CLOSE시 오류가 발생했습니다'
                                       TO  XZUGEROR-I-MSG
                     #ERROR  CO-EBM05001 CO-UBM05001 CO-STAT-ERROR
                     #OKEXIT CO-CHA-08
           END-EVALUATE
           .
       S3800-KJL0042-CLOSE-EXT.
           EXIT.
